>\n咁無人可以睇聖經啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d864229c29ac9cb8ebdf4d5d24fc3df02e2296","tid":183922,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講緊法國文學，德國哲學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後者一定係讀英文，<br />\n前者有部分係中譯比較好<br />\n<br />\n利申：法文好廢</blockquote><br />\n想問下純粹理性批判邊個英譯本最啱初學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用 Allen W. Wood 個版本，網上應該會有<br />\n其他版本都無乜掂過，佢地有d譯法係比較奇怪"},{"pid":"888ffcef31d1200d6344e4239a9d7a56a72f9677","tid":183922,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔睇原文<br />\n等於無睇過</blockquote><br />\n咁無人可以睇聖經啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希伯來文"},{"pid":"34a2f0a9c1b95744133543ad0a9ccd2d7dab0bf1","tid":183922,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔睇原文<br />\n等於無睇過</blockquote><br />\n咁無人可以睇聖經啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希伯來文</blockquote><br />\n據我所知，希伯來文 (例如死海古卷) 嗰啲版本都係譯本。"},{"pid":"1e3481e76d8d9529e6c4d0d36cec988549fab3ea","tid":183922,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"唐吉柯德睇邊個譯本好"},{"pid":"7ead6391c5127a68d23d2973e9d45d1107f64f3a","tid":183922,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔睇原文<br />\n等於無睇過</blockquote><br />\n咁無人可以睇聖經啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希伯來文</blockquote><br />\n據我所知，希伯來文 (例如死海古卷) 嗰啲版本都係譯本。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希伯來聖經唔係希伯來文寫？<br />\n你真係確定？"}]}